---
title: One-Pot American Cannellini Bean & Beef Chilli with Melted Cheddar & Toasty Garlic Panini
description: There are a few things we love about cooking everything in a one pot. First, is the hassle free experience followed up by the magic it creates, blending all those flavours together into a bowl of rich cannellini beans, beef and a saucy base. We love it from start to finish.
